<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="objectType">False 'base'</rs> in relief comprising upper and lower elements; lower element has a <rs type="decoration">bearded male mask</rs> flanked by <rs type="decoration">garland</rs>s in relief. The base was repaired in antiquity, and there are clamp marks.</p>
</div>
